description:
Part 24 of 30. Do you feel discouraged, or lost, or helpless? If so, this unique 3-part series is JUST FOR YOU. Inside the pages of an ancient book (the Bible) you will discover how Jesus Christ (the Savior of the world) gave hope to three very different persons: A leper, and outcast woman, and a demon-possessed man. Believe it or not, Jesus can help you, too! https://youtu.be/soD_VgLU6pE
